entries.femaleVariant: Just wonder why, y'know? Why an NCART train? Couldn't you just blast yourself in the head?
Seriously. Three times I was late for work last week 'cause of them. Be the death of me, I swear.
Aren't they scared? Like, it's gotta hurt, and you don't even know if it'll do the job. But lead? One shot and lights out.
Zackly. 'Stead of stayin' home and outta everyone's biz, they fuck up the whole damn line.
Oh, I get it. Bunch of self-centered assholes!
